---
title: Chicken & Crispy Prosciutto Grain Bowls with Arugula, Shallot & Parmesan
description: Get ready to elevate a classic chicken salad into an irresistible meal that's packed with flavor, texture, and color. You'll toss together juicy grape tomatoes, peppery arugula, and our hearty mixed grain blend with creamy Dijon vinaigrette, then top with warm oregano-seasoned chicken, Parmesan, and the star of the show: crispy fried prosciutto.
